title: Brazil Counted All Its Votes in Hours. It Still Faces Fraud Claims.
description: A report from the military found no voter fraud — but left room for Bolsonaro’s supporters to argue maybe he’d actually won.
dc:creator: Jack Nicas
media:credit: Victor Moriyama for The New York Times
media:description: Supporters of President Jair Bolsonaro demonstrated last week in São Paulo after his electoral defeat, calling for military intervention.
